{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.embedSMℤ₆Toℤ₂\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">embedSMℤ₆Toℤ₂</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The group homomorphism from `StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₆` to `GaugeGroupℤ₂` induced by `embedSM`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.embedSMℤ₆Toℤ₂","kind":"def","line":85,"name":"PatiSalam.embedSMℤ₆Toℤ₂","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L85-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.sm_ℤ₆_factor_through_gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">sm_ℤ₆_factor_through_gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalLemma\">InformalLemma</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The group `StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup` under the homomorphism `embedSM` factors through\nthe subgroup `gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.sm_ℤ₆_factor_through_gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup","kind":"def","line":78,"name":"PatiSalam.sm_ℤ₆_factor_through_gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L78-L83"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.GaugeGroupℤ₂\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupℤ₂</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The gauge group of the Pati-Salam model with a ℤ₂ quotient, i.e., the quotient of `GaugeGroupI`\nby the ℤ₂-subgroup `gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.GaugeGroupℤ₂","kind":"def","line":69,"name":"PatiSalam.GaugeGroupℤ₂","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L69-L76"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The ℤ₂-subgroup of the un-quotiented gauge group which acts trivially on all particles in the\nstandard model, i.e., the ℤ₂-subgroup of `GaugeGroupI` with the non-trivial element `(-1, -1, -1)`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup","kind":"def","line":60,"name":"PatiSalam.gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L60-L67"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.gaugeGroupISpinEquiv\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">gaugeGroupISpinEquiv</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The equivalence between `GaugeGroupI` and `Spin(6) × Spin(4)`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.gaugeGroupISpinEquiv","kind":"def","line":55,"name":"PatiSalam.gaugeGroupISpinEquiv","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L55-L58"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.embedSMℤ₃\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">embedSMℤ₃</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The group embedding from `StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₃` to `GaugeGroupI` induced by `inclSM` by\nquotienting by the kernel `inclSM_ker`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.embedSMℤ₃","kind":"def","line":48,"name":"PatiSalam.embedSMℤ₃","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L48-L53"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.inclSM_ker\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSM_ker</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalLemma\">InformalLemma</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The kernel of the map `inclSM` is equal to the subgroup `StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₃SubGroup`.\n\nSee footnote 10 of https://arxiv.org/pdf/2201.07245\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.inclSM_ker","kind":"def","line":40,"name":"PatiSalam.inclSM_ker","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L40-L46"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.inclSM\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSM</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The homomorphism of the Standard Model gauge group into the Pati-Salam gauge group, i.e., the\ngroup homomorphism `SU(3) × SU(2) × U(1) → SU(4) × SU(2) × SU(2)` taking `(h, g, α)` to\n`(blockdiag (α h, α ^ (-3)), g, diag (α ^ 3, α ^(-3))`.\n\nSee page 54 of https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.inclSM","kind":"def","line":30,"name":"PatiSalam.inclSM","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L30-L38"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.GaugeGroupI\"><span class=\"name\">PatiSalam</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupI</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The gauge group of the Pati-Salam model (unquotiented by ℤ₂), i.e., `SU(4) × SU(2) × SU(2)`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/PatiSalam/Basic.html#PatiSalam.GaugeGroupI","kind":"def","line":25,"name":"PatiSalam.GaugeGroupI","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L25-L28"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.Particles.StandardModel.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"PhysLean.Particles.BeyondTheStandardModel.PatiSalam.Basic"}